<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>

    h1 {
      position: relative;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: slideFade 1.3s ease forwards;
    }

    @keyframes slideFade {
      0% {
        left: -40px;
        opacity: 0;
      }

      100% {
        left: 0;
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    .reveal-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .budget-container {
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 40px 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .budget-card {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      transition: all 0.35s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .dark-card {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #222, #000);
      color: #f0f0f0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      box-shadow:
        0 4px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6),
        inset 0 0 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .dark-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow:
        0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
        inset 0 0 18px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .light-card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff, #f3f3f3);
      color: #222;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      box-shadow:
        0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07),
        inset 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }

    .light-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow:
        0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12),
        inset 0 0 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }

    .toggle-header {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100%;
      color: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .toggle-header h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .toggle-icon {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .toggle-content {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.45s ease;
    }

    .budget-card[aria-expanded="true"] .toggle-icon {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .budget-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
      }

      h1.display-3 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .row.align-items-center {
        text-align: center;
      }

      img {
        max-width: 85%;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .toggle-header h3 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }
    }
    
    .dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      display: inline-block;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-right: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px currentColor;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include ('partials/header') %>
    <div class="container col-xl-10 col-xxl-8 px-4 py-1 mt-1">
      <div class="row align-items-center g-lg-5 py-3">
        <div class="col-lg-7 text-center text-lg-start">
          <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1  mb-4 text-light">Take Control of Your Budget</h1>
          <p class="col-lg-10 fs-5">Budgeting is the first step toward financial freedom. Whether you're saving for a
            goal, paying down debt, or just trying to make your income stretch further, a smart budget helps you take
            control of your money and not the other way around.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto col-lg-5">
          <img src="../static/images/budget.jpg" height="400" width="400" style="border-radius: 20px; margin: 20px;" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="icon-grid">
        <h2 class="pb-2 display-5 fw-bold mt-4" style="text-align: center;">Why Budgeting Matters</h2>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-3 row-cols-lg-4 g-4 py-5">

          <!-- Know Where Your Money Goes -->
          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-compass" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path
                    d="M8 16.016a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 1.962-14.74A1 1 0 0 0 9 0H7a1 1 0 0 0-.962 1.276A7.5 7.5 0 0 0 8 16.016m6.5-7.5a6.5 6.5 0 1 1-13 0 6.5 6.5 0 0 1 13 0" />
                  <path d="m6.94 7.44 4.95-2.83-2.83 4.95-4.949 2.83 2.828-4.95z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">Know Where Your Money Goes</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  Gain a clear picture of your spending habits so you can make informed decisions.
                  Every naira gets accounted for — no surprises.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Stop Overspending & Impulse Buying -->
          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-slash-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14m0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16" />
                  <path d="M11.354 4.646a.5.5 0 0 0-.708 0l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708l6-6a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.708" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">Stop Overspending & Impulse Buying</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  A well-planned budget sets healthy limits and helps you resist unplanned expenses.
                  You stay in control, not your cravings.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Create Room for Saving & Investing -->
          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-piggy-bank" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path
                    d="M5 6.25a.75.75 0 1 1-1.5 0 .75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0m1.138-1.496A6.6 6.6 0 0 1 7.964 4.5c.666 0 1.303.097 1.893.273a.5.5 0 0 0 .286-.958A7.6 7.6 0 0 0 7.964 3.5c-.734 0-1.441.103-2.102.292a.5.5 0 1 0 .276.962" />
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M7.964 1.527c-2.977 0-5.571 1.704-6.32 4.125h-.55A1 1 0 0 0 .11 6.824l.254 1.46a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.478 1.243h.263c.3.513.688.978 1.145 1.382l-.729 2.477a.5.5 0 0 0 .48.641h2a.5.5 0 0 0 .471-.332l.482-1.351c.635.173 1.31.267 2.011.267.707 0 1.388-.095 2.028-.272l.543 1.372a.5.5 0 0 0 .465.316h2a.5.5 0 0 0 .478-.645l-.761-2.506C13.81 9.895 14.5 8.559 14.5 7.069q0-.218-.02-.431c.261-.11.508-.266.705-.444.315.306.815.306.815-.417 0 .223-.5.223-.461-.026a1 1 0 0 0 .09-.255.7.7 0 0 0-.202-.645.58.58 0 0 0-.707-.098.74.74 0 0 0-.375.562c-.024.243.082.48.32.654a2 2 0 0 1-.259.153c-.534-2.664-3.284-4.595-6.442-4.595Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">Create Room for Saving & Investing</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  By allocating money with intention, you can consistently put aside funds for future goals — even from
                  small incomes.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Reduce Stress with a Clear Financial Plan -->
          <div class="col">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.75em" height="1.75em" fill="currentColor"
                  class="bi bi-list-check" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M5 11.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h9a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m0-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h9a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m0-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h9a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5M3.854 2.146a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L2 3.293l1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0m0 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L2 7.293l1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0m0 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708l.146.147 1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-2 fs-5 text-light">Reduce Stress with a Clear Financial Plan</h3>
                <p class="mb-0 text-light">
                  Budgeting removes uncertainty. With a plan in place, you’ll worry less about running out and feel more
                  confident about your choices.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="budget-container">

          <!-- First Card -->
          <div class="budget-card dark-card">
            <button class="toggle-header" aria-expanded="false">
              <h3>Popular Budgeting Methods</h3>
              <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="toggle-content mt-3">
              <ul>
                <li>50/30/20 Rule</li>
                <li>Zero-Based Budgeting</li>
                <li>Envelope System</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Second Card -->
          <div class="budget-card light-card">
            <button class="toggle-header" aria-expanded="false">
              <h3>Tips for Sticking to Your Budget</h3>
              <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="toggle-content mt-3">
              <ul>
                <li>Review Your Budget Weekly</li>
                <li>Use Budgeting Apps</li>
                <li>Set Reminders for Savings & Bills</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="createBudget-section reveal-up py-5">
          <div class="container d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row align-items-center justify-content-between gap-5">
            <div class="col-lg-5 text-center text-lg-start">
              <h2 class="fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">Find Your Perfect Budget Balance</h2>
              <p class="lead text-light opacity-75">
                Adjust your income and watch how the <strong>50/30/20 rule</strong> shapes your spending in real time.
              </p>
              <button class="btn btn-outline-light mt-4 px-4 py-2 rounded-pill">Learn More</button>
            </div>


            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <div class="budget-panel shadow-lg rounded-4 p-4 text-center">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                  <h4 class="mb-0 fw-semibold text-light">Create Your Budget</h4>
                  <button id="resetBtn" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-light rounded-pill px-3">Reset</button>
                </div>

                <div class="slider-container mb-4">
                  <input type="range" id="incomeSlider" min="50000" max="10000000" value="100000" step="100"
                    class="form-range">
                  <p class="income-display mt-2 text-light">₦<span id="incomeValue">100000</span></p>
                </div>

                <div class="chart-wrapper position-relative mx-auto" style="width:260px; height:260px;">
                  <canvas id="budgetChart"></canvas>
                  <div class="chart-center position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle text-light">
                    <p class="mb-0 small opacity-75">Total Budget</p>
                    <h3 class="fw-bold mt-1">₦<span id="centerAmount">100000</span></h3>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="legend d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap gap-3 mt-4">
                  <div><span class="dot needs"></span> Needs (50%)</div>
                  <div><span class="dot wants"></span> Wants (30%)</div>
                  <div><span class="dot savings"></span> Savings (20%)</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="container"
          style="background: linear-gradient(to right, black 50%, white 100%); margin-top: 70px; border-radius: 15px;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
            <h4 class="fst-italic">Did You Know?</h4>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
            <p>"Over 60% of Gen Z feel more in control of their money after 3 months of budgeting."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container" style="margin-top: 50px; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; ">
        <p>“I used to run out of money halfway through the month — now I save without thinking about it."</br>
          <span style="display: flex; justify-content: flex-end;">— Tolu A., Lagos</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include ('partials/footer') %>